Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:25.53,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}令人兴奋难抑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:30.16,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}七色音符  永劫绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.20,0:22:31.41,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}心中忐忑不安
