Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.33,0:22:42.92,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}差不多行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:48.59,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我们终将合二为一  翱翔于天际
